{"tid":1319243,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"各位傳播訊息既咪手請入一入黎","createTime":"2019-07-15T06:14:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T15:37:26.000Z","uid":267978,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fe66d5bdea453bcbbee1489de35a04aa989d8016","tid":1319243,"uid":267978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T06:14:45.000Z","msg":"尋晚係體育館外係好地地，無啦啦有個咪手走黎話大會堂申請左不反對通知書，要走既可以向大會堂方向行。<br />\n<br />\n我明白大家係出於善意既提醒，但你地一講，後面就走左一大半人，拜託，下次可唔可以同前線講左先？<br />\n<br />\n前線決定走，後面既走，<br />\n但可唔可以唔好每次都係因為後面唔夠人，所以前線被逼走呀？<br />\n<br />\n71點解可以齊上齊落呀？係因為煲底、夏慤、龍和都仲有好多手足呀。<br />\n<br />\n後排手足，你地驚，可以散開，但記著有空間要再返黎，be water 呀，唔係be air 一散就冇哂呀！<br />\n<br />\n齊上齊落，一個都不能再讓少！！"},{"pid":"51b387a2ba5f43ffa8abf9e458b01bb0b0fb8f97","tid":1319243,"uid":267978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T06:16:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c9672283a994880545918a6bed87aec4fd8fce0","tid":1319243,"uid":238051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T06:16:16.000Z","msg":"【我冇嘢講2.0】有人冒警！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1319116\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1319116</a><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">有人冒警！\n你扮警察\n涉嫌冒警及傷人\n我地行使公民逮捕權</code></pre>"},{"pid":"4b881219dbaa93ed10574ce6ca24c5f825881f46","tid":1319243,"uid":23738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T06:18:27.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"fd259e1f2d7444a0ebb82274e05ebeb87e5decfb","tid":1319243,"uid":267978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T07:07:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"461666c607e0e924010e925d8ee0d82fa1230e32","tid":1319243,"uid":267978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T07:59:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf0c8e3fe6dc9f10315606d618efe9b4a5ef473e","tid":1319243,"uid":36088,"like":0,"disli